reviewText: If you are a "Dirty Harry" fan this set is a must. wonderful. I wish more of the movies were on DVD.
Title: Clint Eastwood - Cop: (Dirty Harry / Magnum Force / Tightrope)

reviewText: When you figure that all these movies go for about 13-15 dollars each elsewhere, it's a good deal.  Individually, the choice of movies is odd.  While the first two Dirty Harry movies are the better of the series, and entertaining, the psychological horror of tightrope almost feels misplaced.  Perhaps Dirty Harry, tightrope, and another non-dirty harry copy movie would have been better.  Regardless, the movies themselves are all good, and worthy of purchase.
Title: Clint Eastwood - Cop: (Dirty Harry / Magnum Force / Tightrope)

reviewText: It was good. I liked it. It's been years since I saw these. I'm glad to see them digitally remastered on dvd. Dirty Harry is a must gave addition to every library. It was a good value too. I reccomend it to every Clint Eastwood fan.
Title: Clint Eastwood - Cop: (Dirty Harry / Magnum Force / Tightrope)

reviewText: I had never seen these movies before buying this collection. The stories were Clint Eastwood in nature, but I didn't realize that they had all that nudity in them, that wasn't nessesary to get accross the themes. Probably would not have got them if I knew.
